ummit an internationally recognized aviationsafety event chc president and chief executive officer karl fessenden discussed the importance of ensuring that safety continues to remain a top industry priority  chc news chc helicopter celebrates  years of serving customers around the world jan    chc group today announced the beginning of a yearlong celebration of the operator’s year history since its humble beginnings as a crop dusting operation in british columbia in april of  vincent d’rozario joins chc helicopter as regional director asia pacific jan    chc group announced that vincent d’rozario has joined the company as regional director asia pacific chc australia reaches  hour milestone on aw jan    chc group announced it had recently reached the  flight hour milestone on its fleet of aws in australia more news careers join the thousands of experienced and talented people around the globe who work at chc search careers  safety  quality summit register now chc helicopter is proud to supportthe ihst safety initiative chc helicopter sa private company information  bloomberg july    am et airlines company overview of chc helicopter sa snapshot people company overview chc helicopter sa provides helicopter transportation services it offers offshore transportation search and rescue emergency medical and flight training services as well as helicopter maintenance repair and overhaul services the company is headquartered in richmond canada chc helicopter sa operates as a subsidiary of chc helicopter holding sarl  agar driverichmond bc vb acanada phone  key executives for chc helicopter sa mr karl s fessenden chief executive officer age  mr lee eckert chief financial officer age  mr william joseph amelio chief executive officer of helione canada inc and president of helione canada inc age  mr peter bartolotta president  coo  the helicopter svcs business  helione canada inc age  mr larry alexandre president of helione american support llc age  compensation as of fiscal year 